<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Ticket Creation Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .ticket-box { 
            background-color: #abfb33; 
            border: 1px solid #74ef09; 
            border-radius: 5px; 
            padding: 15px; 
            margin: 20px 0; 
        }
        .ticket-info { margin: 20px 0; }
        .steps { margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; color: #666; }
        .status-pending { color: #ff9800; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello {{name}}!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for submitting your registration request. We have successfully created a ticket for your account setup.</p>
        
        <div class="ticket-box">
            <h3>Ticket Created Successfully</h3>
            <div class="ticket-info">
                <p><strong>Ticket ID:</strong> {{ticket_id}}</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-pending">{{status}}</span></p>
                <p><strong>Submitted on:</strong> {{date}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p>Your registration request is currently under review by our admin team. We will process your ticket and notify you once your account has been approved.</p>

        <h3>What happens next:</h3>
        <ol class="steps">
            <li>Our admin team will review your registration details</li>
            <li>You will receive a confirmation email once approved</li>
            <li>After approval, you can log in and browse our packages</li>
            <li>Subscribe to a package that suits your needs</li>
            <li>Complete your vendor profile setup</li>
        </ol>

        <p><strong>Estimated processing time:</strong> 1-2 business days</p>
        
        <p>You can track your ticket status using the Ticket ID provided above. If you have any questions or need to update your information, please contact our support team and reference your ticket number.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>CoreAeration Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>